OL,3,CFlats destroyed in arson attack three
OL,4,Cyears ago to be rebuilt
OL,6,FLeaseholders and residents of an
OL,7,Fapartment block which was destroyed in
OL,8,Fan arson attack three years ago have
OL,9,Fbeen informed construction will begin
OL,10,Fto rebuild properties this year.
OL,12,FTwo men were killed in the fire at
OL,13,FRowe Court in December 2021 and all 24
OL,14,Fflats in the block had to be
OL,15,Fdemolished.
OL,17,FPlanning permission has been granted
OL,18,Fto rebuild the homes but at a charge.
