OL,3,CFlats destroyed in arson attack three
OL,4,Cyears ago to be rebuilt
OL,6,FThe Community Infrastructure Levy
OL,7,F(CIL), which applies to all new
OL,8,Fdevelopments, would mean a fee of
OL,9,F#250,000 is needed to rebuild the
OL,10,Fproperties.
OL,12,FPier Management, which owns the
OL,13,Ffreehold of Rowe Court, say its
OL,14,Finsurers have successfully reached an
OL,15,Fagreement with Reading Borough Council
OL,16,Fto meet the costs required.
OL,18,FIt has now informed residents that
OL,19,Fconstruction will begin in April this
OL,20,Fyear and is expected to be completed
OL,21,Fin summer 2025.
