OL,3,CFlats destroyed in arson attack three
OL,4,Cyears ago to be rebuilt
OL,6,FIn a letter to residents, Pier
OL,7,FManagement said: "Since the fire, we
OL,8,Fhave sought to work with our insurers
OL,9,Fto ensure the destroyed apartment
OL,10,Fblock could be rebuilt as quickly as
OL,11,Fpossible.
OL,13,F"It has taken far longer than we have
OL,14,Fhoped but our insurers have now
OL,15,Freached an agreement with the council
OL,16,Fto meet the cost of these liabilities.
OL,18,F"This means that we can now proceed
OL,19,Fwith the reconstruction of the
OL,20,Fapartments.
