OL,6,F"We appreciate that this has been a
OL,7,Flong and worrying process for
OL,8,Fleaseholders and residents to reach
OL,9,Fthis point, and we share your concern
OL,10,Fand frustration.
OL,12,F"We hope that this development will
OL,13,Fprovide more certainty about the plans
OL,14,Fand timescales for reconstruction."
